quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Miller%20asked%20her%20daughter%20what%20she%20likes%20about%20buying%20skincare%2C%20she%20said%20she%20started%20getting%20interested%20in%20it%20because%20she%20had%20acne%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago.%20It%20cleared%20up%20after%20visiting%20a%20dermatologist%2C%20who%20recommended%20special%20creams%2C%20as%20well%20as%20medicated%20sunscreen%20and%20moisturizer.%20After%20seeing%20the%20effects%2C%20she%20was%20hooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20there's%20a%20special%20occasion%2C%20I%20ask%20my%20parents%20to%20get%20me%20products%2C%20and%20my%20friends%20also%20give%20me%20products%2C%20and%20we%20sometimes%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20about%20%241%2C000%20saved%20up%20last%20year%2C%20but%20I've%20spent%20most%20of%20it%20on%20products%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20money%20left.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20Grant%20Rankin%2C%20an%20educational%20researcher%20and%20author%2C%20told%20BI%20her%2014-year-old%20daughter%2C%20Piper%20Virginia%20Rankin%2C%20also%20spends%20all%20her%20money%20on%20skincare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPiper%20told%20BI%20she%20started%20getting%20interested%20in%20it%20when%20she%20was%2011%2C%20from%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20social%20media%2C%20and%20now%20her%20routine%20makes%20her%20feel%20%26quot%3Bcomfortable%2C%20confident%2C%20and%20hygienic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20she%20gets%20her%20recommendations%20from%20her%20peers%20on%20social%20media%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220329de26-82b2-48e4-8a17-0b0bfbcb3533%5C%22%3EAntiaging%20products%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMedical%20and%20marketing%20experts%20are%20noticing%20a%20skincare%20boom%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValerie%20Aparovich%2C%20a%20certified%20cosmetologist-aesthetician%20and%20the%20science%20team%20lead%20at%20the%20skincare%20product%20scanner%20OnSkin%2C%20told%20BI%20there%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20Gen%20Alpha%20engagement%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20app%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAparovich%20said%20she%20has%20seen%20Gen%20Alpha%20girls%20posting%20%26quot%3Bget%20ready%20with%20me%26quot%3B%20videos%20on%20YouTube%20and%20TikTok%2C%20where%20they%20show%20off%20and%20recommend%20the%20skincare%20products%20they%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShayan%20Cheraghlou%2C%20a%20resident%20physician%20at%20NYU%20School%20of%20Medicine%2C%20told%20BI%20skincare%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20trend%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20has%20observed%20at%20pediatric%20dermatology%20clinics%2C%20but%20with%20a%20concerning%20side%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20kids%20using%20expensive%20vitamin%20C%20serums%20that%20are%20completely%20unnecessary%20for%20their%20age%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20antiaging%20products%2C%20such%20as%20retinol%2C%20that%20can%20damage%20young%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20isn't%20a%20simple%20answer%20to%20why%20anyone%20aged%2014%20and%20under%20is%20interested%20in%20antiaging%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20and%20Rankin's%20daughters%20both%20said%20antiaging%20wasn't%20something%20they%20thought%20about%20during%20their%20beauty%20hauls.%20It%20may%20be%20that%20young%20consumers%20don't%20understand%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20products%20that%20are%20beneficial%20and%20the%20ones%20that%20aren't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20recent%20study%20by%20the%20wellness%20brand%20Thorne%20and%20YouGov%20looked%20into%20Gen%20Alpha's%20sentiment%20around%20aging.%20The%20survey%20of%20nearly%203%2C000%20respondents%20included%20537%20US-based%2013-%20to%2017-year-olds%20who%20were%20asked%20about%20antiaging%2C%20skincare%2C%20and%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%2015%25%20of%20the%20Gen%20Alpha%20kids%20felt%20depressed%20about%20aging%20and%20that%2051%25%20of%20them%20would%20spend%20more%20than%20%24100%20a%20month%20to%20slow%20or%20combat%20aging%2C%20compared%20to%2024%25%20of%20millennials%20and%2015%25%20of%20Gen%20Z.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Alphas%20surveyed%20were%20also%20four%20times%20more%20worried%20about%20wrinkles%20and%20fine%20lines%20than%20other%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c770c18-fdbc-4436-aebb-f79fe15a11a0%5C%22%3EWhere%20influences%20lie%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20that%20Gen%20Alpha%20kids%20are%20learning%20from%20their%20parents%20as%20children%20of%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZoomers%20under%20age%2030%20are%20helping%20drive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbotox-injections-fillers-plastic-surgery-gen-z-social-media-filters-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20injectables%20such%20as%20filler%20and%20Botox%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BI's%20Eve%20Upton-Clark%20reported%2C%20with%20tweakments%20being%20the%20latest%20status%20symbol.%20The%20number%20of%20Botox%20injections%20in%20the%20US%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20jumped%20by%2073%25%20between%202019%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%26quot%3Bworth%20noting%26quot%3B%20that%20millennials%20were%20the%20ones%20to%20popularize%20%26quot%3Bget%20ready%20with%20me%26quot%3B%20content%20and%20makeup%20tutorials%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Dr.%20Geeta%20Yadav%2C%20a%20board-certified%20dermatologist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20FACET%20Dermatology%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20thinks%20children%20in%20Gen%20Alpha%20have%20been%20influenced%20by%20content%20creators%20and%20their%20older%20relatives%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20Y2K%20fashion%20is%20having%20a%20resurgence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Yadav%20said%20she%20thinks%20there%20is%20some%20component%20of%20anxiety%20regarding%20aging%20with%20this%20trend%2C%20and%20older%20generations%20could%20be%20partially%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20came%20of%20age%20in%20the%20early%2000s%20and%20before%20were%20subjected%20to%20horribly%20aggressive%20and%20demeaning%20beauty%20standards%2C%20which%20damaged%20a%20lot%20of%20women's%20self-esteem%C2%A0and%20self-image%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELearning%20not%20to%20pass%20along%20that%20messaging%2C%20which%20is%20deeply%20ingrained%2C%20can%20be%20incredibly%20difficult%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20positive%20shifts%20regarding%20beauty%20standards%2C%20more%20size%20inclusivity%2C%20and%20young%20consumers%20demanding%20more%20skin%20tone%20diversity%20and%20range%20with%20their%20products.%20But%20%26quot%3Baging%20is%20one%20hurdle%20that%20we%20have%20yet%20to%20cross%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Yadav%20said%2C%20especially%20with%20so%20many%20advances%20in%20skincare%20that%20make%20people%20look%20younger%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20millennials%20continue%20to%20age%20and%20continue%20to%20obsess%20about%20looking%20young%2C%20that%20can%20send%20a%20very%20loud%20message%20to%20Gen%20Alpha%20about%20aging%20and%20beauty%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Forsyth%2C%20a%20consumer%20retail%20and%20cyber%20security%20expert%20at%20AFRG%2C%20told%20BI%20she%20doesn't%20believe%20Gen%20Alphas%20are%20particularly%20interested%20in%20antiaging%2C%20but%20brands%20are%20pushing%20their%20messaging%20onto%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20raises%20eyebrows%20but%20also%20prompts%20serious%20questions%20about%20the%20influences%20shaping%20this%20young%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForsyth%20said%20children%2C%20sometimes%20as%20young%20as%20seven%20or%20eight%2C%20are%20posting%20about%20their%20skincare%20routines.%20Some%20tweens%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Fsephora-tweens-teens-drunk-elephant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoke%20with%20Mashable%20about%20their%20adult%20skincare%20habits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20one%2C%20named%20Maeve%2C%20suggested%20the%20fad%20was%20more%20about%20having%20what%20everyone%20else%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20know%20I%20wanted%20it%2C%20and%20then%20when%20I%20see%20that%20someone%20else%20has%20it%20and%20how%20they%20use%20it%2C%20I%20realize%20it's%20something%20I'd%20actually%20use%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20may%20be%20that%20they're%20doing%20much%20of%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20of%20marketing%20campaigns%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20necessarily%20that%20they're%20looking%20toward%20older%20people%20to%20influence%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Forsyth%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20influencing%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-alpha-is-obsessed-with-skincare-aging-anxiety-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718102363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6655defe20abc1efe8fde7c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-alpha-is-obsessed-with-skincare-aging-anxiety-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gen%20Alpha%20tweens%20are%20only%2014%20and%20under%2C%20but%20they%20are%20already%20obsessed%20with%20expensive%20skincare%20they%20don't%20need.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40insider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-alpha-is-obsessed-with-skincare-aging-anxiety-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CD%20and%20Savings%20Rates%20Today%3A%20Start%20Earning%20More%20Interest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcd-rates-savings-rates-today-tuesday-11-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffi