ver%20your%20fears%20about%20big%20bad%20AI%2C%20give%20you%20a%20cup%20of%20warm%20milk%2C%20tuck%20you%20into%20your%20cozy%20bed%2C%20and%20stroke%20your%20hair%20until%20you%20fall%20asleep.%20At%20the%20keynote%20presentation%20for%20its%20yearly%20developer%20conference%20on%20Monday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-wwdc-event-live-updates-keynote-announcements-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20finally%20unveiled%20its%20AI%20intentions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Google's%20recent%20event%20that%20showed%20off%20futurist%20things%20like%20AI%20search%20results%20(which%20ended%20up%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-answers-overviews-fixed-social-media-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eembarrassment%3C%2Fa%3E)%20or%20OpenAI's%20keynote%20in%20May%20%E2%80%94%20which%20caused%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-scarlett-johansson-voice-defense-sam-altman-washington-post-chatgpt-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escandal%20over%20the%20similarity%20of%20the%20company's%20voice%20assistant%20to%20Scarlett%20Johansson's%20voice%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20where%20the%20abilities%20of%20its%20technology%20seemed%20uncanny%20and%20freaky%20%E2%80%94%20Apple's%20demonstration%20was%20familiar%20and%20seemed%20practical%2C%20like%20something%20you%20could%20actually%20%3Cem%3Euse%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(One%20couldn't%20help%20notice%20Apple%20actually%20had%20the%20%3Cem%3Ereal%3C%2Fem%3E%20Scarlett%20Johansson%20in%20its%20keynote%20%E2%80%94%20in%20clips%20for%20%26quot%3BFly%20Me%20to%20the%20Moon%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-tv-plus-shows%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20TV%2B%3C%2Fa%3E%20movie.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224255bf1d-0ae8-41bc-b328-724bd44b2718%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20'artificial%20intelligence%2C'%20it's%20'Apple%20Intelligence'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20Apple's%20new%20AI%20world%2C%20we%20start%20with%20one%20rule%3A%20Don't%20call%20it%20%26quot%3Bartificial%20intelligence.%26quot%3B%20It's%20%26quot%3BApple%20Intelligence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%2C%20you%20ask%3F%20Haha!%20Don't%20worry%20about%20the%20details%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-wwdc-openai-partnership-ai-strategy-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%20deal%20with%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E!%20Just%20focus%20on%20the%20nice%2C%20pleasing%20things%20it%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20Intelligence%20can%20perform%20simple%20and%20useful%20functions.%20One%20demo%20involved%20someone%20needing%20to%20pick%20up%20her%20mom%20from%20the%20airport.%20Siri%20can%20pull%20up%20flight%20details%20from%20an%20email%2C%20pull%20up%20tracking%2C%20and%20find%20lunch%20reservation%20details%20that%20were%20messaged%20in%20a%20text.%20Helpful!%20Not%20intimidating!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20feature%20is%20in%20the%20Mail%20app.%20Apple%20isn't%20suggesting%20that%20it%20can%20write%20an%20email%20for%20you%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20can%20help%20you%20lightly%20revise%20an%20email%20to%20be%20in%20a%20different%20tone.%20(Options%20include%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bconcise%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfriendly.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20giving%20you%20the%20baby%20steps%20of%20generative%20AI%20here%20%E2%80%94%20not%20trying%20to%20suggest%20it%20can%20do%20the%20work%20of%20humans%2C%20just%20brush%20it%20up%20a%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20sort%20your%20emails%20into%20categories%3A%20primary%2C%20transactions%2C%20updates%2C%20or%20promotions%2C%20which%20is%20great%20(but%20also%20%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgmail-update-fix-email-tabbed-inbox-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGmail%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20a%20decade).%20Additionally%2C%20it%20will%20use%20AI%20to%20prioritize%20your%20notifications%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20enable%20a%20%26quot%3Breduce%20notifications%26quot%3B%20mode%20(ahhhh%2C%20yes!).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221771a5f7-b247-4dfb-be88-8cafb068fe78%5C%22%3EApple%20Intelligence%20wasn't%20mindblowing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20of%20the%20other%20generative%20things%20were%20purely%20goofy%2Fcutesy%2C%20like%20the%20AI%20version%20of%20Memoji.%20With%20this%20tool%2C%20you%20can%20create%20a%20cartoon%20image%20of%20your%20friend%20to%20wish%20them%20a%20happy%20birthday.%20It's%20truly%20stupid.%20Please%20know%20that%20if%20you%20send%20me%20a%20generative%20Memoji%20of%20myself%2C%20we%20are%20now%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20small%20enhancements%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20already%20could%20exist%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20like%20recording%20and%20transcribing%20phone%20calls%20or%20photo-editing%20tools%20to%20remove%20an%20object%20from%20the%20background%20of%20a%20picture.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapples-iphone-is-about-to-get-more-like-an-android-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%20users%20are%20probably%20laughing%20right%20now%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENothing%20was%20mindblowing%20or%20a%20totally%20radical%20new%20way%20of%20using%20%3Cs%3Eartificial%3C%2Fs%3E%20Apple%20Intelligence.%20There%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bwow%26quot%3B%20feature%20or%20jaw-dropping%20moment.%20It%20was%20just%20a%20bunch%20of%20small%2C%20helpful%20things%20that%20will%20make%20iPhones%20and%20computers%20a%20little%20more%20convenient%20to%20do%20things%20they're%20already%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0778138-3fde-4a7c-aa47-83267d35d4ad%5C%22%3EAI%20for%20normies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20probably%20a%20good%20way%20of%20introducing%20AI%20to%20the%20iPhone-owning%20normies%20of%20the%20world.%20People%20are%20%E2%8