.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fios-18-brings-support-for-call-recording-rcs-messaging-and-more-details-124061100479_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fios-18-brings-support-for-call-recording-rcs-messaging-and-more-details-124061100479_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Book%20Review%20%7C%20The%20Dirty%20Dozen%3A%20The%20Story%20Of%20India's%2012%20Biggest%20Corporate%20Defaulters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Published%20by%20PanMacmillan%20India%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Published%20by%20PanMacmillan%20India%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbd3dmfng_dirty-dozen_625x300_11_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublished%20by%20PanMacmillan%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20Kongo%20Gumi%20Co%20Limited%2C%20which%20specialised%20in%20constructing%20Buddhist%20temples%2C%20is%20considered%20the%20world's%20longest-running%20family%20business.%20It%20was%20established%20in%20578%20AD%2C%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Golden%20Age%20of%20the%20Guptas%20was%20nearing%20its%20end%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Mayan%20civilisation%20was%20still%20flourishing%20in%20parts%20of%20Central%20America%2C%20and%20the%20erstwhile%20Roman%20empire%20had%20started%20disintegrating.%20Kongo%20Gumi%20had%20an%20independent%20run%20for%201%2C429%20years.%20In%202006%2C%20the%20company%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20unable%20to%20repay%20its%20debts.%20It%20subsequently%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Takamatsu%20Construction%20Group%20and%20continues%20to%20operate%20as%20a%20subsidiary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20IBC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kongo%20Gumi%20episode%20epitomises%20the%20double-edged%20nature%20of%20the%20insolvency%20and%20bankruptcy%20process.%20A%20company's%20inability%20to%20pay%20back%20its%20debts%20would%20eventually%20lead%20to%20closure%20of%20the%20business%2C%20and%20asset%20forfeiture.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20if%20handled%20adeptly%2C%20a%20business%20could%20continue%20its%20run%2C%20albeit%20with%20a%20different%20promoter%2C%20or%20group%20of%20shareholders.%20India's%20Insolvency%20and%20Bankruptcy%20Code%20(IBC)%2C%20which%20was%20enacted%20in%20May%202016%2C%20was%20a%20spirited%20response%20on%20similar%20lines%20to%20tackle%20the%20twin%20balance%20sheet%20syndrome%20that%20impacted%20the%20economy%2C%20engulfing%20both%20the%20banking%20and%20the%20corporate%20sectors.%20Over-leveraged%20businesses%20were%20finding%20it%20hard%20to%20pay%20the%20interest%20due%20on%20outstanding%20debt.%20Banks%20were%20saddled%20with%20non-performing%20assets%2C%20impacting%20their%20profitability%2C%20and%20constraining%20fresh%20lending.%20To%20break%20the%20logjam%2C%20IBC%2C%20with%20the%20full%20backing%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20and%20the%20Central%20government%2C%20took%20on%20the%20top%2012%20biggest%20corporate%20defaulters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20catchy%20title%20given%20by%20seasoned%20business%20journalist%20N.%20Sundaresha%20Subramanian%C2%A0to%20these%20'bad%20boys'%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Dirty%20Dozen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20may%20appear%20a%20misnomer.%20Unlike%20the%20characters%20in%20the%20iconic%20Hollywood%20movie%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20heroic%20about%20this%20bunch.%20Their%20actions%20and%20deeds%20that%20landed%20themselves%20and%20the%20lending%20ecosystem%20in%20such%20a%20mess%20largely%20stemmed%20from%20corporate%20greed%2C%20corruption%2C%20political%20influence%20peddling%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20plain%20bad%20luck.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20many%20captains%20of%20Corporate%20India%20would%20not%20be%20proud%20of%20the%20conduct%20of%20some%20of%20their%20peers%20in%20creating%20the%20distressed%20assets%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Big%20Twelve'%20Cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inability%20-%20in%20some%20cases%20bordering%20on%20incompetence%20-%20of%20the%20lending%20institutions%20to%20adhere%20to%20even%20rudimentary%20financial%20checks%20and%20balances%20while%20ever-greening%20loan%20books%20exposed%20the%20weakness%20of%20the%20regulatory%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20eight%20years%20of%20its%20operations%2C%20the%20IBC%20has%20'brought%20about%20a%20shift%20in%20debtor-creditor%20relationships%2C%20leading%20to%20ownership%20changes%20in%20many%20large%20companies%26quot%3B%2C%20points%20out%20Dr%20M.S.%20Sahoo%2C%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Insolvency%20and%20Bankruptcy%20Board%20of%20India%2C%20in%20the%20Foreword.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20'Big%20Twelve'%20managed%20to%20recover%20convincingly%2C%20others%20had%20to%20be%20liquidated%2C%20and%20a%20few%20are%20still%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%20Their%20resolutions%20tested%20the%20guardrails%20of%20the%20Code%2C%20setting%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20bankruptcy%20regime's%20operational%20success.%20A%20recent%20study%20by%20IIM-Ahmedabad%20finds%20that%20post-resolution%2C%20the%20companies%20have%20witnessed%20substantial%20improvement%20in%20their%20financial%20performance%20and%20governance%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubramanian%C2%A0puts%20the%20spotlight%20on%20how%20individual%20business%20groups%20and%20their%20promoters%20landed%20up%20in%20this%20infamous%20club.%20He%20chronicles%20the%20travails%20of%20the%20Code%20in%20each%20of%20the%20'Big%20Twelve'%20cases%20in%20finding%20the%20resolution.%20In%20some%20instances%2C%20the%20journey%20becomes%20more%20important%20than%20the%20destination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20Were%20Financing%20The%20Promoter'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20sections.%20The%20first%20part%20gives%20a%20political-economic%20context%20to%20India's%20burgeoning%20stressed%20asset%20scenario%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20which%20snowballed%20into%20a%20banking%20and%20financial%20crisis%20post-2008%20following%20the%20global%20financial%20meltdown.%20The%20helplessness%20of%20the%20bankers%20in%20mitigating%20the%20fallout%20of%20portent%20financial%20crises%20is%20well-captured%20in%20the%20following%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Joint%20Lenders%20Forum%20that%20was%20called%20to%20decide%20the%20course%20of%20action%20to%20deal%20with%20some%20stressed%20assets%2C%20the%20promoter%20of%20a%20small%20company%20tells%20a%20room%20full%20of%20public%20sector%20bankers%20that%20he%20has%20stashed%20enough%20money%20to%20take%20care%20of%20himself%20if%20things%20went%20wrong%2C%20bragging%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20pay-off%20even%20jailors.%20In%20another%20instance%2C%20which%20involved%20the%20financing%20of%20an%20infrastructure%20project%2C%20a%20retired%20bank%20official%20concedes%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20not%20financing%20the%20project.%20We%20were%20financing%20the%20promoter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20instances%20of%20auditors%20looking%20the%20other%20way%20when%20promoters%20divert%20funds%20for%20personal%20use%2C%20or%20bankers%20ignoring%20red%20flags%20raised%20by%20auditors%2C%20or%20cases%20of%20blatant%20misuse%20of%20RBI%20circulars%20and%20schemes.%20Then%20there%20are%20governance%20challenges%20to%20deal%20with.%20As%20per%20a%20study%20conducted%20in%20January%202023%2C%20around%2035%25%20of%20director%20board%20positions%20are%20lying%20vacant%20in%20public%20sector%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nirav%20Modi%20and%20Vijay%20Mallya%20cases%20taught%20the%20bankers%20some%20hard%20lessons.%20They%20did%20not%20want%20a%20repeat%20of%20what%20Modi%20and%20Mallya%20did%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20laid%20the%20ground%20for%20how%20the%20banking%20fraternity%20rallied%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20'Big%20Twelve'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Abuse%20Of%20Regulatory%20Mechanisms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrative%20picks%20up%20pace%20in%20Section%20II%2C%20which%20delves%20into%20the%20actions%20of%20delinquent%20promoters%20and%20how%20they%20use%20and%20abuse%20the%20legal%2C%20regulatory%20and%20administrative%20machinery%20to%20their%20advantage%20as%20their%20companies%20turn%20defaulters.%20The%20chapters%20in%20this%20section%20go%20into%20the%20back%20story%20of%20each%20of%20the%20promoters%2C%20chronicling%20the%20circumstances%20of%20their%20rise%20and%20fall.%20Perhaps%20the%20author%20could%20have%20elaborated%20a%20bit%20more%20about%20the%20current%20state%20of%20each%20of%20the%20promoters.%20One%20is%20left%20wondering%20as%20to%20what%20some%20of%20them%20are%20up%20to%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20common%20thread%20through%20their%20respective%20narratives%20is%20that%20the%20'red%20flags'%20of%20financial%20distress%20were%20there%20to%20be%20seen%20and%20picked%20up%2C%20just%20that%20someone%20somewhere%20chose%20to%20ignore%20or%20looked%20the%20other%20way.%20Though%20each%20of%20the%20accounts%20is%20gripping%2C%20at%20times%20one%20tends%20to%20lose%20the%20thread%20of%20the%20narrative%20in%20the%20details%20and%20descriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Devils%20Get%20Their%20Due%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20section%20looks%20at%20the%20institutional%20response%20to%20the%20stressed%20asset%20crisis%20and%20also%20how%20it%20has%20changed%20-%20or%20not%20changed%20-%20the%20behaviour%20of%20some%20corporate%20groups%20that%20continue%20to%20be%20highly%20leveraged.%20The%20response%20of%20the%20regulators%2C%20banks%2C%20and%20policymakers%20has%20evolved%20over%20time.%20They%20recognise%20that%20the%20Code's%20road%20to%20success%20in%20balancing%20the%20creditor-debtor%20relationship%20is%20always%20under%20construction%2C%20as%20Sahoo%20puts%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsolvency%20applications%20for%20the%20initiation%20of%20the%20IBC%20process%20against%2027%2C514%20companies%20-%20with%20an%20aggregate%20default%20of%20Rs%209.74%20trillion%20-%20were%20withdrawn%20before%20admission.%20As%20Sahoo%20points%20out%2C%20perhaps%20the%20best%20use%20of%20the%20IBC%20is%20not%20using%20it%20at%20all.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Dirty%20Dozen%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0gives%20the%20Devils%20their%20due%20as%20they%20became%20the%20test%20case%20for%20checking%20the%20efficacy%20and%20efficiency%20of%20the%20Code.%20It%20chronicles%20the%20saga%20of%20their%20rise%2C%20fall%2C%20demise%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20a%20comeback%20-%20and%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20attendant%20ecosystem.%20The%20winners%20from%20this%20churn%3A%20the%20'good'%20spirit%20of%20enterprise%20and%20rule%20of%20law.%20Something%20worth%20fighting%20for%2C%20anytime%2C%20always.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sudipto%20Dey%20is%20a%20senior%20business%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718094120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm3k2seug_dirty-dozen_625x300_11_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-dirty-dozen-the-story-of-indias-12-biggest-corporate-defaulters-5865366%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22N.%20Sundaresha%20Subramanian%20chronicles%20the%20travails%20of%20the%20IBC%20in%20each%20of%20the%20'Big%20Twelve'%20cases%20in%20finding%20the%20resolution.%20In%20some%20instances%2C%20the%20journey%20becomes%20more%20important%20than%20the%20destination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-dirty-dozen-the-story-of-indias-12-biggest-corporate-defaulters-5865366%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyper-realistic%20humanoid%20robots%20could%20be%20used%20in%20psychotherapy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22