5%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fpulp-fiction-producer-stacey-sher-honored-locarno-film-festival-1236033105%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chirag%20Paswan%20Steps%20Into%20Father's%20Shoes%2C%20Shares%20Vision%20For%20His%20Ministry%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20chief%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20who%20is%20among%20the%20youngest%20faces%20in%20the%20latest%20Modi%20cabinet%20or%20Modi%203.0%2C%20has%20shared%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20food%20processing%20ministry%20assigned%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20belongs%20to%20the%20food%20processing%20sector%20and%20will%20help%20increase%20farmers'%20income%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20after%20assuming%20charge%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20new%20role%20entrusted%20to%20him%2C%20the%2041-year-old%20cabinet%20minister%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wants%20to%20take%20the%20department%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20the%20involvement%20of%20food%20processing%20globally%2C%20India's%20involvement%20is%20comparatively%20very%20less%20than%20global%20involvement%20in%20the%20food%20processing%20industry.%20In%20the%20coming%20times%2C%20there%20is%20unlimited%20scope%20in%20this%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Paswan%2C%20emphasising%20the%20potential%20in%20India's%20food%20processing%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shared%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20department%20that%20was%20helmed%20by%20his%20father%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20until%20his%20death%20in%202020.%20His%20uncle%2C%20Pashupati%20Paras%2C%20headed%20it%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20own%20vision%20is%20focused%20on%20establishing%20more%20processing%20units%20so%20that%20farmers%20can%20get%20an%20appropriate%20amount%20for%20their%20produce%20and%20their%20income%20increases%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20processing%20sector%20in%20foreign%20countries%20are%20more%20advanced%2C%20said%20the%20newly%20appointed%20minister%20and%20hoped%20to%20achieve%20similar%20progress%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20foreign%20countries%2C%20several%20works%20are%20done%20through%20processing%20units%20only%2C%20whereas%20we%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20it%20yet.%20So%2C%20I%20hope%2C%20just%20like%20my%20father%2C%20the%20late%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20I%20will%20contribute%20100%20per%20cent%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20PM%20Modi%20has%20assured%20him%20of%20support%20in%20elevating%20the%20department's%20status.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20met%20him%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20assured%20me%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20we%20will%20take%20this%20department%20to%20new%20heights%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718091540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5mv59r2_chirag-paswan-ians_625x300_11_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-steps-into-fathers-shoes-shares-vision-for-his-ministry-5865254%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20chief%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20who%20is%20among%20the%20youngest%20faces%20in%20the%20latest%20Modi%20cabinet%20or%20Modi%203.0%2C%20has%20shared%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20food%20processing%20ministry%20assigned%20to%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-steps-into-fathers-shoes-shares-vision-for-his-ministry-5865254%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-steps-into-fathers-shoes-shares-vision-for-his-ministry-5865254%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchirag-paswan-steps-into-fathers-shoes-shares-vision-for-his-ministry-5865254%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSanctity%20Of%20Exam%20Affected...%20Need%20Answers%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20NEET-UG%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20centre%20and%20NTA%2C%20or%20National%20Testing%20Agency%2C%20over%20a%20petition%20seeking%20to%20cancel%20results%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20-%20an%20ultra-competitive%20entrance%20test%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%20-%20amid%20allegations%20the%20paper%20was%20leaked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20that%20simple...%20that%20because%20you%20have%20done%20it%20(held%20the%20exam)%20it%20is%20sacrosanct%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20told%20the%20NTA%2C%20%26quot%3BSanctity%20of%20(the%20examination)%20has%20been%20affected...%20so%20we%20need%20answers.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20though%2C%20said%20counselling%20for%20admissions%20will%20continue.%20Justices%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20stopping%20counselling%26quot%3B.%20The%20matter%20was%20then%20posted%20to%20July%208%20and%20will%20be%20heard%20with%20a%20plea%20filed%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20fresh%20petition%20in%20the%20ongoing%20row%20over%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20results%20that%20claim%20discrepancies%20in%20scores%20and%20alleged%20preferential%20treatment%20to%20some%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20asked%20for%20the%20scores%20from%20the%20May%205%20exam%20to%20be%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20also%20asked%20for%20a%20fresh%20exam%20to%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20-%20from%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20-%20have%20claimed%20variances%20in%20grant%20of%20grace%20marks%2C%20for%20which%20they%20say%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20defined%20logic%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20drawn%20the%20court's%20attention%20to%20%26quot%3Bstatistically%20impossible%26quot%3B%20marks%2C%20including%20students%20scoring%20the%20maximum%20-%20720%20of%20720.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20no%20defined%20logic%20for%20grace%20marks%20given%20(and)%20no%20list%20has%20been%20shared%20as%20per%20given%20grace%20marks.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20reason%20for%20awarding%20grace%20marks%20is%20'wastage%20of%20time'...%20but%20this%20was%20never%20disclosed%20in%20information%20bulletin%20before%20the%20exam%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioners%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20fact%2067%20students%20from%20one%20particular%20coaching%20centre%20got%20a%20full%20720%20marks%2C%20and%20also%20that%20a%20provisional%20answer%20key%20released%20by%20the%20NTA%20had%20been%20contested%20by%20over%2013%2C000%20students%20as%20the%20problem%20pointed%20to%20a%20different%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20dangers%20of%20cheating%20in%20a%20medical%20test%2C%20the%20plea%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20field%20requires%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20and%20medical%20knowledge...%20cheating%20or%20using%20unfair%20means%20to%20pass%20an%20exam%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20competence%20and%20endanger%20lives%20of%20patients.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20also%20noted%20that%20cheating%20in%20exams%20%26quot%3Bundermines%20the%20principles%20of%20meritocracy%20and%20equal%20opportunities%2C%20which%20are%20essential%20for%20social%20mobility%20and%20fairness%20in%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20perpetuates%20inequalities%20by%20favoring%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20to%20pay%20for%20leaked%20exam%20papers%20or%20engage%20in%20fraudulent%20activities%2C%20while%20disadvantaging%20those%20who%20rely%20on%20their%20hard%20work%20and%20merit%20to%20succeed%20and%20the%20same%20also%20impacts%20the%20society%20as%20a%20whole%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2017%2C%20while%20the%20bench%20led%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20was%20hearing%20a%20similar%20plea%2C%20the%20court%20issued%20a%20notice%20but%20did%20not%20halt%20declaration%20of%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20NTA%20has%20decided%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20will%20analyse%20the%20grievances%20of%201%2C600%20students%20who%20have%20already%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET%202024%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718091540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9ijrm348_supreme-court_625x300_15_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-exam-paper-leak-supreme-court-sanctity-of-exam-affected-need-answers-supreme-court-on-neet-ug-row-5865003%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20centre%20and%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20over%20a%20petition%20seeking%20to%20cancel%20results%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20-%20entrance%20test%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%20-%20amid%20allegations%20the%20paper%20was%20leaked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-exam-paper-leak-supreme-court-sanctity-of-exam-affected-need-answers-supreme-court-on-neet-ug-row-5865003%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-exam-paper-leak-supreme-court-sanctity-of-exam-affected-need-answers-supreme-court-on-neet-ug-row-5865003%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-exam-paper-leak-supreme-court-sanctity-of-exam-affected-need-answers-supreme-court-on-neet-ug-row-5865003%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kangana%20wants%20to%20normalise%20obsessive%20work%20culture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3