i-ashok-vaidya-aram-shankar-gajanan-swati-snacks-jai-maharashtra-shivaji-park%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Use%20Cardboard%20Boxes%20to%20Protect%20Your%20Plants%20From%20The%20Heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20you%20receive%20a%20package%2C%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20the%20cardboard%20waste%3F%20In%20India%2C%20households%2C%20itinerant%20waste%20merchants%2C%20and%20garbage%20collectors%20jointly%20recover%202.4%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0921344915300082%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHouseholds%252C%2520itinerant%2520waste%2520merchants%2520and%2Ctonnes%2520of%2520plastic%252C%2520more%2520than1.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4.3%20million%20tonnes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20cardboard%20and%20mixed%20paper%20annually.%20Overall%2C%2030%E2%80%9360%20percent%20of%20all%20paper%20and%20cardboard%20is%20recycled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata-based%20Krishna%20Khuku%20has%20found%20an%20innovative%20way%20to%20transform%20used%20delivery%20boxes%20into%20plant%20protectors.%20She%20shares%20three%20possible%20and%20easy%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20As%20a%20protective%20layer%20against%20heat%20waves%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20says%20cardboard%20protects%20plants%20from%20heat%20waves%20while%20keeping%20the%20soil%20moist%20and%20preventing%20pest%20attacks.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F186864%2Fmumbai-girl-recycles-waste-organic-compost-raises-lakhs-dharavi-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUsing%20cardboard%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereduces%20evaporation%20from%20the%20top%20exposed%20soil%2C%20preventing%20it%20from%20drying%20out%20by%20holding%20the%20moisture%20in.%20It%20promotes%20more%20steady%20soil%20temperature%20overall.%20It%20will%20suppress%20w