ion%2C%20which%20takes%20about%2015%20days%2C%20we%20fertiliise%20the%20soil%20with%20%3Cem%3Ejivamrit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20technique%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Ejivamrit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Jaswinder%20asks%20to%20start%20with%20five%20kg%20of%20cow%20dung%20and%20mix%20it%20with%20seven%20litres%20of%20cow%20urine%20in%20a%20200-litre%20drum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20this%2C%20add%201.5%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Ebesan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chickpea%20flour)%20and%20jaggery%20each.%20Fill%20the%20water%20to%20the%20rim%20and%20stir%20the%20mixture.%20Take%2040%20litres%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejivamrit%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20fertilise%20one%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ranjit%20shares%20his%20secrets%20to%20preparing%20natural%20insecticides%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Ebrahmastra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eagnihastra%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20enhance%20plant%20disease%20resistance%2C%20provide%20nutrients%2C%20and%20control%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20make%20%3Cem%3Ebrahmastra%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Etake%20one%20kg%20of%20four%20kinds%20of%20leaves%20and%20neem.%20Crush%20them%20and%20add%20in%20four%20litres%20of%20cow%20urine%20and%20dung.%20Boil%20the%20mixture.%20After%20two%20boils%2C%20cool%20it%20down%20and%20strain%20it%20into%20a%20tank.%20It%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20be%20sprayed%20on%20crops%20after%2048%20hours.%20You%20can%20also%20store%20this%20insecticide%20for%20six%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1-1717133339.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20makes%20their%20own%20natural%20fertilisers%20using%20simple%20ingredients%20like%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22htt